Dr. Zeidan was amazing. I was a PRM for her and she is super caring and compassionate. Helps you succeed in every way she can. Super pleasant to work with and might be a PRM again for her if my schedule works out. Easy A as a student and as a PRM.

This is Spring 2022 and her first semester here btw.

I'm a Peer mentor for Dr. Z's Cellex class (298). Literally the nicest woman I've ever met. She is super understanding and kind and respectful. You really can't ask for more. Interesting research and great prof. Go take.

Absolutely lovely human being—the content might be hard but you will get an A practically no matter what so long as you put the work in. Dr. Z is truly a sweetheart and just a really kind and intelligent human being. She clearly cares deeply about her research and her students! Highly recommend her stream (FIRE CellEX) to any upcoming FIRE198 natural sciences students.
